2. Debt to Asset Ratio:

   - Total Assets = $19,501,451.49
   - Debt to Asset Ratio = $3,389,719.66 / $19,501,451.49 = 0.174 = 0.17

3. Gross Profit Margin:
   - Gross Profit Margin = Gross Profit / Total Revenue
   - Gross Profit = $287,062.51
   - Total Revenue = $791,992.51
   - Gross Profit Margin = $287,062.51 / $791,992.51 = 0.3624 = 36.24%
